dict.string:
Harold is a sweet hunk of a cat who prefers being the only cat! He is looking to be king of his castle!
Harold is neutered, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Harold, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Amber is a sweet pastel calico who is looking for a forever home. Gorgeous and funny, Amber is sure to win your heart.
She is neutered, up to date on shots and healthy!
To learn more about Amber or meet her please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com.

Dumpling is a little kitten with a BIG personality! Totally beautiful in every way!
For more info or to meet Dumpling, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Mr. Palmer is gorgeous gorgeous gorgeous and sweet sweet sweet!
He is neutered, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Mr. Palmer, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Trey is a sweet kitten who is shy at first but warms up quickly. Would love a patient caring person to adopt him and allow his confidence to blossom.
Trey is 6-7 months old, neutered, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Trey, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Georgianna is a gorgeous young kitty with personality and charm! Seriously... look at that face!
Georgianna is spayed, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Georgianna, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Tom Tom is a beautiful female cat. She is loving and sweet and ready to find her forever home. She is about 4 months old and as charming as kittens come.
She is neutered, up to date on shots and healthy!
To learn more about Tom Tom or meet her please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com.

Luther is a super stud. Mellow loving personality, he is looking to charm his way into your heart and your home. Please consider adopting Luther today!
Luther is neutered and vaccinated. Luther is FIV positive but very healthy.
For more info or to meet Luther, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Edie loves being held and adored. A total mush of a cat. Perfect in every way! Please consider adopting Edie today!
She will be spayed and tested in the next few weeks.
For more info or to meet Edie, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Amanda is a beautiful cat with the sweetest personality. She has Eosinophilic Granuloma, which has caused an ulcer on her front lip, which sort of looks like a cleft lip. But her loving personality makes up for this unique look!
She is spayed, vaccinated, and approximately 1 year old. She is FIV positive.
For more information or to meet Amanda please contact lois@neighborhoodcats.org.

Claudia is a sweet kitten looking for a loving home.
She is spayed, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Claudia, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Myrtle is a gentle cat with beautiful markings of mostly white with a calico tail and temples. Sweet and loving, she is shy at first but loves to be pet and adored. She was recently rescued from ACC and is looking for her much deserved fairytale ending.
Myrtle is about 4 years old, spayed, vaccinated and FIV/FeLV negative
For more info or to meet Myrtle, please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Alice is a sad eyed girl from Bed Stuy. She is a bit shy at first but warms up quickly when one picks her up and purrs on contact! Alice is looking for the happy ending she deserves.
Alice is under a year, spayed, vaccinated and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Alice, please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Rebecca is an fun loving 9 month old kitty who didn't like living in a cage so is being fostered by a volunteer of Kitty Loft. She is a sweet as cats come but doesn't care for other cats.
If you are looking to adore and be adored by one special cat, Rebecca is for you!
She is neutered, vaccinated, and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Rebecca, contact Brooke at bjacobsphoto@gmail.com
Chester is a loving boy who enjoys attention. He is from a recent TNR project in Red Hook and has white hairs all through out his black body. He is quite the looker!

Brutus is a handsome young man with the energy and playfulness of a kitten. Loves toys and to run run run! He was rescued from the Lower East Side of Manhattan and is looking for his forever home.
Brutus is about 1.5 yrs old, neutered, FIV/FeLV neg and up to date on vaccines.
For more info or to meet Brutus, contact Annie; kittyloft@gmail.com

Clyde is a big guy with a big heart. He is a low key cat seeking your company on HIS terms. He was rescued from ACC â€“ he was found in a closet after the owner was evicted and left him behind. He is looking for his 2nd chance.
Clyde is about 5 years old, neutered, vaccinated, FIV/FeLV negative.
For more information or to meet Clyde contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Wilbur was a shy kitten who has been fostered and is doing great and coming out of his shell. He loves to be cuddled and adored. He really enjoys living in a home and hopes he can find one soon!
He is spayed, up to date on shots and healthy!
To learn more about Wilbur or meet him please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com.

Monty is a wonderfully handsome young adult who loves to play and loves other cats. Rescued as a kitten along with his brother Hugo â€“ he is looking for the chance to steal your heart.
Monty is about 1.5 years old, neutered, vaccinated and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Monty please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

The Dude is another Kitty Loft favorite! He has a LARGE personality and a hip shaking walk. He is pure purrfect love.
He is 1-2 years old, neutered, up to date on vaccines. While he is FIV positive, he is healthy and sure to stay that way in his forever home without the stress of life on the streets.
For more info on FIV: http://www.bestfriends.org/theanimals/petcare/cats_fiv.cfm
For more info or to meet The Dude, contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Hugo is a character. We've had Hugo and his two brother since they were kittens. Always getting into something, Hugo has a lot of energy â€“ loves to play, loves other cats, especially his brother Monty and is pure entertainment! He is looking for his 1st real home. Hugo was rescued from the streets of Williamsburg.
Hugo is about 1.5 years old, neutered, vaccinated and FIV/FeLV negative.
For more info or to meet Hugo please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com

Felicia is looking for her forever home. Sweet, neutered, up to date on shots and healthy! Her sisters left today and she is ready for a home of her own.
If you are interested in adopting Felicia please contact Annie at kittyloft@gmail.com
